@startuml

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #495057
    ArrowColor #495057
    FontColor #212529
}
skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    BorderColor #6C757D
}
skinparam activity {
    BackgroundColor #F8F9FA
    BorderColor #495057
    ArrowColor #495057
    FontColor #212529
    DiamondBackgroundColor #FFF3CD
    DiamondBorderColor #856404
    StartColor #212529
    EndColor #212529
    BarColor #495057
}
skinparam swimlane {
    BorderColor #6C757D
    TitleBackgroundColor #E9ECEF
    TitleFontColor #212529
    TitleFontSize 13
}
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E9ECEF
skinparam noteBorderColor #6C757D

title AI Service Provider Bootstrap

|Laravel Application|
start
:Boot application;
:Instantiate **AiServiceProvider**;

|AiServiceProvider|
:Call **register()**;

fork
  :Bind **AiManager** as scoped singleton\n<i>app->scoped(AiManager::class,\n fn => new AiManager($app))</i>;
fork again
  :Bind **ConversationStore**\nas singleton\n→ **DatabaseConversationStore**;
fork again
  :Merge default config\n<i>mergeConfigFrom(\n  config/ai.php, 'ai'\n)</i>;
end fork

:Call **boot()**;

if (app->runningInConsole()?) then (yes)
  fork
    :Call **registerCommands()**;
    :Register Artisan commands\n• **MakeAgentCommand** (make:agent)\n• **MakeAgentMiddlewareCommand** (make:agent-middleware)\n• **MakeToolCommand** (make:tool)\n<i>[ChatCommand disabled / commented out]</i>;
  fork again
    :Call **registerPublishing()**;
    fork
      :Publish **config/ai.php**\n→ config_path('ai.php')\n<i>tags: ai, ai-config</i>;
    fork again
      :Publish **stubs**\n• agent.stub\n• structured-agent.stub\n• tool.stub\n• agent-middleware.stub\n→ base_path('stubs/')\n<i>tag: ai-stubs</i>;
    fork again
      :Publish **migrations**\n→ database_path('migrations')\n<i>publishesMigrations()</i>;
    end fork
  end fork
else (no)
  note right
    Commands and publishable
    resources are skipped outside
    of the console context.
  end note
endif

fork
  :Register **Stringable::macro('toEmbeddings')**\n<i>Closure: builds Embeddings request,\nsets optional dimensions / cache / timeout,\ncalls generate(provider, model)</i>;
fork again
  :Register **Collection::macro('rerank')**\n<i>Closure: resolves items via Closure|array|string,\ncalls Reranking::of()->limit()->rerank(),\nmaps results by index</i>;
end fork

|Laravel Application|
:AiServiceProvider fully bootstrapped;
note right
  **AiManager** is scoped per HTTP request.
  **ConversationStore** is a global singleton.
  Macros are always available.
end note

stop

@enduml
